V0444_01_00_00_0.text:
My name is Dumon.
The one who is going to win this Duel.

V0444_01_00_01_0.text:
I am Dumon!
I will defend the glory of Barian World!

V0444_01_00_02_0.text:
I am Dumon!
One of the Seven Barian Emperors!

V0444_01_00_03_0.text: I will not allow you to steal any more Numbers!

V0444_01_00_04_0.text: There can never be peace between us, Yuma.

V0444_01_00_04_1.text: My mission is to destroy Astral World.

V0444_01_00_05_0.text:
Reginald Kastle, I am Dumon.
The one who will defeat you.

V0444_01_00_06_0.text: You have betrayed us for the last time, Vector!

V0444_01_00_07_0.text:
Vector!
You are nothing but a treacherous fiend!

V0444_01_00_08_0.text:
We have no reason to quarrel.
But if we must, I will win!

V0444_01_00_09_0.text: I am your faithful friend, but I can be your greatest enemy!

V0444_01_00_10_0.text:
Don Thousand!
I will never allow you to consume me!

V0444_03_00_00_0.text: You managed to survive this far, but not any further!

V0444_03_00_01_0.text: By the end of this turn, you will have no LP left!

V0444_03_00_03_0.text: You will not stop me from executing my strategy!

V0444_03_00_04_0.text: I have no choice but to do what I must!

V0444_03_00_05_0.text: If I do not end you this turn, I will have no chance to win.

V0444_05_00_00_0.text: This draw will guide me to victory!

V0444_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0444_07_09_01_0.text: This is the card I Set!

V0444_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0444_16_00_00_0.text: It seems you have reached your end!

V0444_16_00_01_0.text: This single strike will erase the rest of your LP!

V0444_21_00_00_0.text: You withstood my onslaught, but it is only a matter of time.

V0444_21_00_01_0.text: Surviving is a far cry from winning!

V0444_21_00_02_0.text: With that, I end my turn!

V0444_21_00_04_0.text:
Argh...
This cannot continue for much longer...

V0444_28_00_00_0.text:
I will do anything to protect the Barians!
Anything!

V0444_28_00_02_0.text:
You fought well.
But it is now time for you to rest!

V0444_28_00_03_0.text: I wish we could have met under different circumstances.

V0444_28_00_04_0.text: Behind your wild words, I sense true skill.

V0444_28_00_05_0.text: Good or bad, I cherish every moment we spent together.

V0444_28_00_06_0.text: You and Nash mean more to me than you realize, Marin.

V0444_28_00_08_0.text: Never act on your own without my permission.

V0444_28_00_09_0.text: This is not the time to be fighting each other!

V0444_29_00_00_0.text: You were much more powerful than I expected.

V0444_29_00_01_0.text:
This was a ferocious battle.
Well done.

V0444_29_00_02_0.text:
This cannot be...
How could I lose...

V0444_29_00_04_0.text: You remind me of a dear friend of mine...

V0444_29_00_05_0.text: You are wiser than you seem - similar to someone I know...

V0444_29_00_06_0.text: Galaxy-Eyes Tachyon Dragon is truly terrifying.

V0444_29_00_08_0.text: There are no lows you will not sink to, Vector!

V0444_29_00_09_1.text: It is clear that we can use your help.

V0444_29_00_10_1.text:
Marin, Nash...
I am so glad to have known you.

V0444_29_00_11_0.text: Use your power for Barian World.

V0444_29_00_12_0.text: Why do you need to consume us when you are already almighty?

V0444_31_00_01_0.text: You were waiting for just this single moment!

V0444_33_00_00_0.text: Only my special technique can defeat you!

V0444_33_00_01_0.text: I never expected I had to use this against you...

V0444_33_00_02_0.text: I am left with no choice!

V0444_43_00_00_0.text:
Dumon!
The protector of Barian World!

V0444_30_00_01_0.text: Your soul must be rotten to resort to such tactics!

V0444_30_00_02_0.text: Nash, if you were only here...

V0444_34_00_00_0.text: Oh no! I can no longer unleash my true strength!

V0444_34_00_01_0.text: How ruthless of you to destroy all these cards...

V0444_34_00_02_0.text: I must use my special technique to defeat you!

V0444_34_00_03_0.text: Despite the odds, I will keep fighting!

V0444_34_00_04_0.text: Calm down. Watching and waiting is a viable tactic.

V0444_34_00_05_0.text: Say whatever you want! I need to win this Duel!

V0444_34_00_07_0.text: I wanted to have a fair Duel - not a Duel like this.

V0444_34_00_08_0.text: Legend says that we need to trust each other!

V0444_34_00_09_0.text: Why are you surprised, my friend?

V0444_34_00_10_0.text: You will not escape! Even if I have to follow you forever!

V0444_34_00_11_0.text: I will never forgive you for what you have done!

V0444_35_00_00_0.text: I am the Barian Warrior, Dumon!

V0444_35_00_01_0.text: I, Dumon, will defend Barian World!

V0444_36_00_02_0.text: You must do whatever it takes to win!

V0444_36_00_03_0.text:
Nash, my friend!
Bring us victory!

V0444_36_00_04_0.text: This should be easy for you, Nash.

V0444_36_00_07_0.text:
Marin!
Let us show them our teamwork!

V0444_36_00_08_0.text: Marin, I am sorry that I am so powerless.

V0444_36_00_09_0.text: I am counting on you, Mizar.

V0444_36_00_10_0.text: Only you can get us out of this mess.

V0444_36_00_11_0.text: I trust in your abilities, Alito.

V0444_36_00_13_0.text:
What are you waiting for?
Go, Vector!

Barian Untopia!

Seventh Ascension!

Rank-Up-Magic Quick Chaos!

Reincarnation of the Seventh Emperors!

V0444_08_00_16_0.text: I activate my Continuous Trap, Seventh Eternity!

V0444_08_00_18_0.text: I activate my Trap, Intrigue Shield!

V0444_08_00_19_0.text: I activate my Quick-Play Spell, Satellarknight Skybridge!

V0444_08_00_20_0.text:
I activate my Quick-Play Spell!
Tellarknight Genesis!

V0444_08_00_21_0.text:
I activate my Equip Spell!
Stellarknight Alpha!

V0444_08_00_22_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Spell!
Constellar Tellarknights!

V0444_08_00_24_0.text:
I activate my Field Spell!
Hexatellarknight!

I activate my Counter Trap!
Stellarnova Alpha!

V0444_08_00_27_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Stellarnova Wave!

V0444_37_00_03_1.text: Awaken from your ancient sleep to soar among the skies!

V0444_13_00_07_0.text: Set your eyes on Star Seraph Scepter!

V0444_13_00_15_0.text: I present to you Darktellarknight Batlamyus!
